Discouraging proliferation is a pointless waste of time as it can never ultimately be successful. It has the opposite effect. Just like the war on drugs only feeds the trade by driving up the value of the product. Embracing nuclear technology would probably lead to a decrease in proliferation. It also offers an opportunity to break out of a viscious circle. Nuclear power can give us space. <br>
<br>
