Interesting analogy. Medicinal research today is more narrowly targeted at fighting the symptoms of disease than finding a cure. There is no money in wiping out diseases. Ofcourse, treating only the symptoms of a disease is not a solution to the underlying cause. In that respect it is not disimilar to attempts at suppressing nuclear technology. <br>
<br>
